        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Capping Drug Costs for Seniors Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill reduces the annual out-of-pocket spending threshold, and eliminates beneficiary cost-sharing above this threshold, under the Medicare prescription drug benefit.</p>]]></text>
